name: Storming Area 51 (Correia de Brito)
description:
The day has come. It's September 20, 2019, the day of the raid. Join forces with Elon Musk to storm the most mysterious place in the USA. Choose between six  classes, from Kyle and Naruto-runner to the mythical JC Denton, set your skills and manage your items and abilities in this meme-powered adventure. The secrets of Area 51 await  you.

(Note: There are some  audio mistakes still being fixed. It's advised to reload the page after reaching one ending, as not doing so may cause the music to overlap. To avoid problems with prompt commands, run the game on the Itch.io browser version.)
